{"cid": "UgzF_4JrR9_IH0R7t0R4AaABAg", "text": "It's so exciting to find out things that even zebras don't know, nature always has a way of surprising us! 🌍", "time": "1 month ago", "author": "@WildlifeWorld8386", "channel": "UCiIWQu7NjnmtNOM6evZGdUQ", "votes": "0", "replies": "", "photo": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/VO3QVC2l2Qkjn4jk9O03W4I41dNbc-UqfdsuEp0Lz4rgZdfaRNTC5tS4fsqqtSxwXremKWh_=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj", "heart": false, "reply": false, "time_parsed": 1762968729.9035}
{"cid": "UgzdH1eCnq2CaKa8aEx4AaABAg", "text": "What an incredible journey! 🦓 Watching these zebras fight through danger, stick together, and keep moving is such a powerful reminder of nature’s resilience and family bonds. BBC Earth never fails to capture the beauty and struggle of life in the wild. Truly inspiring!", "time": "1 month ago", "author": "@animalAIscience", "channel": "UCC3drHeSd2pf991PFzD9W3g", "votes": "7", "replies": "", "photo": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/zhiPPHsnPcIf90TyR5bStFcsbH_ED3x8qPy61YKS549Hh6DfM-RCFrGaQOBp_JF1zDJTGsSH7A=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj", "heart": false, "reply": false, "time_parsed": 1762968729.9044}
