{"cid": "UgxPf_EdxQuuoHBWmnJ4AaABAg", "text": "Impresionante documental, muestra la belleza y los desafíos reales de la vida salvaje africana.", "time": "1 month ago", "author": "@VidaAnimal-TV", "channel": "UCvaWDX2cA7fyCSz0adzTN4Q", "votes": "1", "replies": "", "photo": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/lUVBfrXCBmVuYzlr31FA28pGgJOWFDk_8oiUkynYjjvc-TSRJkmhu-uEdn-XtS4eIXUB33wtMA=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj", "heart": false, "reply": false, "time_parsed": 1762968729.906109}
{"cid": "Ugyh8ldKk631_foZRuJ4AaABAg", "text": "No painkillers out there, no bandages. You either manage to stay alive or you don't. No restaurants for the lions either. Nature is beautiful but also brutal.", "time": "1 month ago", "author": "@blucat4", "channel": "UCmkhEsnWvK1TIcSJ0UlaGbg", "votes": "1", "replies": "", "photo": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/qv_rh7vaEKGSEnA6Gd5j27__Xc9JhldSxoZQ8aQ5VxvkCbLPVXeEFLZWMA-SsNXwUEE6vcFnCQ=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj", "heart": false, "reply": false, "time_parsed": 1762968729.906944}
