{"cid": "UgyP-NkRzTnBhTU22z14AaABAg", "text": "A breathtaking journey of endurance and survival in the wild! 🦓🌍🔥", "time": "1 month ago", "author": "@WildlifeLegends96", "channel": "UCkPTPwZmUNwcGSSuphLHN4w", "votes": "0", "replies": "", "photo": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/CJOSS_veROQHPZLVOZcrtYnxJzlZpLRYvlYDTHu_Nd7Ol0gzlAvXKZaRGywiG8IiD9nfqRt7Tw=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj", "heart": false, "reply": false, "time_parsed": 1762968729.910278}
{"cid": "UgzuHU2cpW3RO7A9WJh4AaABAg", "text": "I can’t believe how far the zebra travels just to survive… nature’s great migrations are both beautiful and cruel at the same time.", "time": "1 month ago", "author": "@야생매", "channel": "UCROdwNhwvU_2ruzwGHX7b4g", "votes": "6", "replies": "", "photo": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/aAAD7sDAtk4wvWdg9CBpcvFySQsY5C4eLuXLrYD6BV4tG7Z_1ehYfmWiqbglA0ZK_qfwnvqUNCg=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj", "heart": false, "reply": false, "time_parsed": 1762968729.911215}
{"cid": "Ugy6mgmkgsLILi8CE694AaABAg", "text": "Interessantes Video. Gruß Jürgen 🤠", "time": "1 month ago", "author": "@jürgensenke", "channel": "UCvtmyW505Bmg8i2b5UAI7RA", "votes": "2", "replies": "", "photo": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/jmaTme4Rzs3Be4XrYE5IThCpz-ZbfWDKc5vX6OltOE1ht0bev7mgm9C4AE5VU1B22VXhM906Tg=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj", "heart": false, "reply": false, "time_parsed": 1762968729.912061}
{"cid": "UgwUCjbM8Qb66DGPWnV4AaABAg", "text": "This is the Earth at its finest. May we be wise enough to preserve it for those who come after us. 🌿", "time": "1 month ago", "author": "@동물의왕국DC", "channel": "UCY-wEOxYpnpbpeOqkF-1qYg", "votes": "16", "replies": "", "photo": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/Fna64zg4ypI6IWyyqzovLjL92TQtdEetcgP5lvAEr_ngvBq1o7ezUkofPsxME4hvqn1kuvF2kw=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj", "heart": false, "reply": false, "time_parsed": 1762968730.180965}
{"cid": "UgxElp9M-QUK5TDv9Ih4AaABAg", "text": "This whole journey is insane, but the Socks storyline is chef's kiss. Losing the GPS, finding the faint signal, and then seeing that tiny newborn foal—I literally yelled, \"YES!\" What an absolute warrior. Do you think the new baby scent made her a bigger target right after the birth?", "time": "1 month ago", "author": "@naturesmomentstv", "channel": "UC7R28A21ABhLnvY9bRed8MQ", "votes": "0", "replies": "", "photo": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/XZJKh_EcN_mk0TMqPQ_vENTBuBXYIc2Pgyef9vg_flYTUccpQOqPA4EzWOIbGPcf8oDc8YMKqQ=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj", "heart": false, "reply": false, "time_parsed": 1762968730.182115}
