{"cid": "Ugxx4rVMTFniCUz3dXh4AaABAg", "text": "I hope the baby Zebra heals.", "time": "1 month ago", "author": "@zahirmurji", "channel": "UCHFmP6fJzMwT1KBOwNcILTw", "votes": "3", "replies": "", "photo": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_ldYuJxAwX4wwUerLvPikoMhftSt3X2LVYtRn-a0pKpcpE=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj", "heart": false, "reply": false, "time_parsed": 1762968730.183819}
{"cid": "UgxMGetrpPj0rIoXxv94AaABAg", "text": "Can we take a moment to appreciate how researchers track every heartbeat of this migration? Absolutely fascinating.\nWhen nature writes its own endings, they’re always perfect. That tiny foal was worth every mile.", "time": "1 month ago", "author": "@WildUs-x7s", "channel": "UCZydGyRSqyflVj8L4x15aEg", "votes": "2", "replies": "1", "photo": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/QtbkJtpDgNslvQzWI3GXr2yKBtRPUZm7P-0wagctMRtX6d2nnnPuEQRGAbx4njOsppDWj1qx3w=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj", "heart": false, "reply": false, "time_parsed": 1762968730.184673}
{"cid": "Ugy07-IxBXuHW73gmnx4AaABAg", "text": "Wow, I didn’t expect to get emotional over zebras, but this story really got me. Hearing about Janet, Spirit, and Socks felt like following the journey of old friends through danger, loss, and survival. I can’t imagine how hard that migration must be — predators, exhaustion, and the constant uncertainty of who will make it. When the team finally picked up Socks’s signal, I actually felt relieved, like I was holding my breath for her the whole time. Nature is so raw and real, and moments like this remind me how strong these animals are. I really hope the rest of Janet’s herd is safe somewhere out there. Has anyone been following this migration series from the start?", "time": "1 month ago", "author": "@AnimalPrimeHub", "channel": "UCdnLVpxTo2icAy0PwYSQdUg", "votes": "13", "replies": "1", "photo": "https://yt3.ggpht.com/oWZaOQYpHSSu9UKX81Ab6WMVm5EqZvFIwhmsIgBo5J57jVi4PFiEyK_poaGPZ-BQKQ0KWdFqdA=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj", "heart": false, "reply": false, "time_parsed": 1762968730.185599}
